meta.description: This phylogeny shows publicly available SARS-CoV-2 sequences recovered from domestic cats since the start of the COVID-19 pandemic through December 2021, in addition to a random sample of human-derived sequences collected at the same times in the same geographic areas.
meta.title: Genomic epidemiology of novel coronavirus - Global subsampling
